articles.title: Visual Analytics
articles.description: Hello there, I am Karishma Yadav. Welcome to my Website!
articles.contents: This website is built using the distill package in R. It is composed of my submissions for the Visual Analytics module taught by Professor Kam Tin Seong at the Singapore Management University. I hope you like my work!
